Dynamic Angular Application:

If view interacts with the controller for dynamic data, then such type of application called as dynamic angular application.

Steps to create the Dynamic Angular application:
-------------------------------------------------

1. download angular framework by using bower.

2. load the angular framework

3. declare the logical name for the web application

Ex.

    ng-app = "app"

4. declare the controller

Ex.
    <div ng-controller="ctrl">

    </div>

5. implement the controller

//we need to create the app module object.
var app = angular.module("app",[]);

//implement the controller
app.controller("ctrl",function(){

});